  "text": "Here we used two strategies for single-cell A3243G mtDNA mutation load quantization: (1) physical isolation of individual cells by single-cell sorting, followed by closed-tube, real-time fluorescence PCR load measurement; and (2) bi-color in situ mtDNA genotyping by Padlock/rolling circle amplification (Padlock-RCA) [CITATION_1] , in combination with image analysis for quantification purposes.",
